This paper discusses principles of Solomonoff Induction and AIXI, which are related to artificial intelligence, machine learning, information theory, and computational complexity. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.AI, followed by cs.LG (machine learning), cs.IT (information theory), cs.CC (computational complexity), and cs.CR (cryptography and security).
